{"tid":190974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呢個世界要以暴易暴先至運作到","createTime":"2017-04-07T13:13:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-07T13:44:31.000Z","uid":20241,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"804406dfab22892f71e75d705507f260397f991d","tid":190974,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T13:13:16.000Z","msg":"話說我屋企唔知上下左右邊一戶啦<br />\n成日剁野，仲要木帖板大力剁落去個種聲<br />\n持續幾年，假日聽到真係好抆<br />\n咁我問過曬，無人認，又話佢地都聽到<br />\n有個仲話要食安眠藥<br />\n我本身諗住話送條毛巾俾佢地墊住剁細聲d大家好做<br />\n但無功而還<br />\n咁我尋日買左個幾舊水藍牙喇叭放窗口<br />\n條撚樣一剁我就戴耳罩播youtube個d 2000hz既高音波地圖炮<br />\n而家個世界安靜曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f15ae853f25834727d0d1be0adb0b31f7d419e2","tid":190974,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T13:16:38.000Z","msg":"勁"},{"pid":"2662b8fb4e87698e90dd2de968157cba6bc22259","tid":190974,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T13:16:48.000Z","msg":"謝霆鋒住你樓上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34e4d0d06a9e7fe472e00201680feeaa3967aaff","tid":190974,"uid":35814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T13:18:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>謝霆鋒住你樓上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19de177960606e28d00dc25514eeed56ef55b243","tid":190974,"uid":4874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T13:19:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>謝霆鋒住你樓上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cee39699b44762e3610bc3fd1036da4fc1da357","tid":190974,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T13:19:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>謝霆鋒住你樓上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br